    "tokenName": "UNI",
    "description": "Uniswap V2 is an automated market maker (AMM) DEX that uses constant-product (x*y=k) liquidity pools for permissionless token swaps on Ethereum. All 9 protocol contracts are immutable with no upgradeability. Governance (GovernorBravo with a 48-hour Timelock) exists but controls only the protocol fee switch via FeeToSetter and FeeTo — it cannot modify the core swap or liquidity logic. Total liquidity across all pairs is $748.60M."
